  dialogue:
  - H-Hello? Is there something there?
  - It's so dark I can hardly see...
  - I wish my lamp wasn't so shoddy...
  - Wait! If you managed to find me, I must be free!
  - Thank you, wooly creature!
  - I will escape as soon as my legs can carry me!
  - I've been standing here a long time...
  - Hmm? There was a gap in that wall the whole time?...
  - I knew that.
